26
00:03:26,003 --> 00:03:29,268
I'II... stand by my own words...

27
00:03:30,941 --> 00:03:32,966
That's my Ninja Way!

28
00:03:38,749 --> 00:03:39,807
<i>I'll...</i>

29
00:03:42,186 --> 00:03:43,346
<i>stand...</i>

30
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,282
<i>by my own...</i>

31
00:03:49,326 --> 00:03:50,384
<i>words!</i>

32
00:03:51,462 --> 00:03:54,761
<i>That's my...Ninja Way...</i>

33
00:03:57,167 --> 00:03:58,862
