no matter what!

37
00:04:10,214 --> 00:04:11,146
<i>Naruto...</i>

38
00:04:15,886 --> 00:04:20,653
A brat who knows nothing
shouldn't lecture arrogantly!

39
00:04:21,392 --> 00:04:26,420
People are born burdened with
an inherent destiny that they cannot defy.

40
00:04:32,669 --> 00:04:35,399
<i>Neji...live...</i>

41
00:04:35,906 --> 00:04:38,067
<i>You're a man who is blessed</i>
<i>with Hyuga ability</i>

42
00:04:38,142 --> 00:04:40,838
<i>more than anyone in the family...</i>

43
00:04:44,248 --> 00:04:48,207
<i>I wanted you...to be born</i>
<i>into the head family...</i>

44
00:04:53,757 --> 00:04:55,588
You can't possibly understand

45
00:04:55,659 --> 00:04:59,789
the destiny of being burdened with
a mark that cannot be wiped off for life!

46
00:05:42,372 --> 00:05:43,339
Yeah...

47
00:05:44,675 --> 00:05:46,142
I do understand it.

48
00:05:49,012 --> 00:05:52,470
So... what of it?

49
00:05:53,417 --> 00:05:54,884
<i>This brat!</i>

50
00:05:57,788 --> 00:05:59,483
