up blood with that in mind!

56
00:06:28,218 --> 00:06:29,583
You too!

57
00:06:30,754 --> 00:06:32,722
The branch family that
protects the head family...

58
00:06:32,789 --> 00:06:35,189
Doing all that to Hinata
just because it's an exam.

59
