77
00:08:17,928 --> 00:08:21,625
<i>You must extract and utilize, at any time,</i>

78
00:08:21,698 --> 00:08:25,600
<i>the other huge Chakra that</i>
<i>has rested inside you from the start...</i>

79
00:08:27,504 --> 00:08:31,201
<i>That's it. The Nine Tailed Fox Chakra...</i>
<i>I'll use that...</i>

80
00:08:43,887 --> 00:08:47,618
