89
00:09:32,269 --> 00:09:33,361
<i>No matter what...</i>

90
00:09:34,071 --> 00:09:38,974
<i>Oh, yeah! Be sure to come</i>
<i>watch me kick that Neji's butt!</i>

91
00:09:44,948 --> 00:09:48,076
